# Installing Java & three ways to run it

## Install — Eclipse Temurin (OpenJDK)

```bash
brew install --cask temurin   # JDK 21 LTS
brew install jbang maven gradle
```

- Verify in a new shell: `java --version`, `javac --version`

## Three on-ramps

- **`jshell`** — "what does this expression do?" the cheapest feedback loop
- **`jbang`** — one file you keep around; deps in a top comment
- **Maven / Gradle** — real projects: many files, deps, tests, build — what **Spring** uses
